      <div class="py-2">
        <text class="text-lg">
          A <code>HACKTIV8</code> Grad from 2020. I develop full stack web applications preferably with Typescript. 
          I spent most of my time on my computer. Currently running
          i5-10400f with RX 6600, and 32gb ram is still not enough to run WSL.
        </text>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <div class="pb-3">
          <text class="text-lg">
            This website can exist thanks to the open source community for the tools
            and the templates that were given freely.
          </text>
        </div>
        <div>
          <a href="https://github.com/manuelernestog/astro-modern-personal-website" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline">
            Get This website's template
